Class PHPArray.Node<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • PHPArray.Node<V>
  • Enclosing class:
    PHPArray<V>

    private class PHPArray.Node<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a (singly) linked list element used by PHPArray. Each node contains data for a (Key, Value) pair, and a reference property to link the next list element.
